  "description": "<h3><strong>Able to commit at least 6 consecutive months.</strong></h3>\n<h3>One-time bonus of $200 after 6 months consecutive work</h3>\n<h3><u><strong>PERMANENT PART-TIME</strong></u></h3>\n<h3><u><strong>7hrs a day+ 45mins break(meal provided), 5 days per week: (2:15PM to 10:00PM Shift)</strong></u></h3>\n<h3>Contact Person: Ms Lyn 91548053</h3>\n<h3>Job Responsibilities:-<br>\n- Serve the customer according to SUBWAY standard</h3>\n<h3>- Food preparation including bread and cookie baking<br>\n- Ensure food storage and preparation areas are maintained according to Health and Safety and Audit standards<br>\n- Comply with Food Code of Practice<br>\n- Complete daily and weekly cleaning schedules<br>\n- Follow security and safety procedures<br>\n- Maintain a safe working environment for employees and customers<br>\n- Work as a team member<br>\n- Deliver a high standard of service when dealing with products, sales and catering for customer needs</h3>\n<h3>- Opening/Closing the shop<br>\n<br>\nStart immediately if you have already have a valid food hygiene certificate, TDAP &amp; MMR Vaccine<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nWorking Location:-<br>\nSUBWAY<br>\nChangi General Hospital<br>\n2 Simei St 3<br>\n#01-03 (next to Lobby B)<br>\nSingapore 529889</h3>\n<h3><br></h3>\n<p><br></p>",
